OL,3,CGaza medic's fear after 33 relatives
OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FHamza explains how, during one shift
OL,8,Fat the hospital last month, he got
OL,9,Fnews that a relative's house had been
OL,10,Fhit in an Israeli strike. ITV News
OL,11,FCorrespondent Rachel Younger reports
OL,13,FIn the patched-together buildings of
OL,14,Fthe Indonesian hospital in Gaza, an
OL,15,Fimpossibly young medic does his best
OL,16,Fto save the wounded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
