OL,3,CGaza medic's fear after 33 relatives
OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FHamza wears surgical scrubs but is
OL,8,Fjust 21 years old. A medical student
OL,9,Fat Al Azhar University, he's been
OL,10,Fthrust by the war, ahead of time, into
OL,11,Fthe brutal reality of life-saving
OL,12,Fsurgery.
OL,14,FThe Strip is now desperately short of
OL,15,Fmedics. The UN estimates more than
OL,16,F1,400 healthcare workers have been
OL,17,Fkilled since the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
