OL,3,CGaza medic's fear after 33 relatives
OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FFor the past month, Hamza has been
OL,8,Ftrying to document a little of what he
OL,9,Fsees, as a volunteer medic, because he
OL,10,Fbelieves time is running out for him
OL,11,Ftoo.
OL,13,FIsrael has closed Gaza to
OL,14,Finternational journalists, so we can't
OL,15,Freach him ourselves. But over the
OL,16,Fcourse of four weeks, on the videos he
OL,17,Fsends us, you can see his resilience
OL,18,Fcrumbling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
