OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FIn the early hours of Thursday,
OL,8,Fslumped beyond exhaustion, he told us
OL,9,Fhis neighbour had asked what would
OL,10,Fhappen to them.
OL,12,F"I told him our death is only a matter
OL,13,Fof time," he said. "But we must do
OL,14,Fsomething good with whatever time we
OL,15,Fhave left."
