OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FSince the ceasefire collapsed on March
OL,8,F18, Israel has intensified its bombing
OL,9,Fcampaign. With only 22 of its 36
OL,10,Fhospitals still functioning, none of
OL,11,Fthem fully, Hamza works through the
OL,12,Fnight to cope with the injured.
OL,14,FIn the past year and a half, he says
OL,15,Fhe has lost 81 family members.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
