OL,3,CGaza medic's fear after 33 relatives
OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FAs he records his most recent video
OL,8,Fmessage, explosions sound around him,
OL,9,Fso loud they make you jump as you
OL,10,Fwatch. Hamza doesn't bat an eyelid,
OL,11,Fbut he looks pale and in shock, which
OL,12,Fis little surprise.
OL,14,FOvernight, a building close to his
OL,15,Fhome was bombed by the Israelis. He
OL,16,Fsends us videos, which show young
OL,17,Fchildren trapped in rubble. Hamza
OL,18,Fexplains that they are more of his
OL,19,Fyoung relatives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
