OL,7,FHe speaks quickly, quietly, with
OL,8,Flittle emotion as he describes how a
OL,9,Fhouse about 200 metres away from him
OL,10,Fwas targeted.
OL,12,F"I realised that there were injuries
OL,13,Fand murders. I could hear the sound of
OL,14,Fa hammer smashing through the rubble,
OL,15,Ftrying to rescue those trapped
OL,16,Funderneath".
