OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FBy the time the ambulances arrived in
OL,8,Fthe morning, the tragedy was clear.
OL,9,F"We lost 18 martyrs," Hamza records
OL,10,Fdully. "Most of them were women and
OL,11,Fchildren."
OL,13,FOn bad days at the Indonesian
OL,14,Fhospital, he finds himself treating
OL,15,Fhis family and friends. On the worst
OL,16,Fdays, they die before he can treat
OL,17,Fthem.
