OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FHamza explains how, on one shift last
OL,8,Fmonth, he got news at 4pm that a
OL,9,Frelative's house had been hit.J"A four-
OL,10,Fstory building, a back-to-residence,
OL,11,Fhad been bombed," he said.
OL,13,FWe ask him for photos of happier
OL,14,Ftimes. He sends snaps from his phone
OL,15,Fof a young family gathered around a
OL,16,Fbicycle. Another of his grandmothers,
OL,17,Fsmiling proudly as she hugs a younger
OL,18,FHamza.
