OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FThey didn't survive the bombing.
OL,8,F"About 15 people were martyred," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "My sister's children, my
OL,10,Fcousin, my grandmother, my uncle, his
OL,11,Fwife and their children."
OL,13,FHe tells us he's had to delete photos
OL,14,Fof his beloved twin baby nephews,
OL,15,Fbecause it hurt too much to look at
OL,16,Fthem. He doesn't say how his sister,
OL,17,Fbereft of her children, is doing. He
OL,18,Fdoesn't need to.
