OL,3,CGaza medic's fear after 33 relatives
OL,4,Cincluding babies killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FIn theory, hospitals like his should
OL,8,Fbe the Strip's safest places, but they
OL,9,Fare regularly hit by Israel's missiles.
OL,11,F"I'm afraid the hospital could be
OL,12,Fbombed at any moment," he says.
OL,14,F"Afraid that I might be the next. But
OL,15,Fdespite the fear, we keep working. We
OL,16,Fcontinue to provide treatment, and we
OL,17,Fwill remain here until our last breath
OL,18,Fand until the last drop of hope."
